WEBVTT

00:00:58.463 --> 00:01:00.615
Would you like to share
your story with me?"

00:01:01.530 --> 00:01:03.368
Farai begins,

00:01:03.392 --> 00:01:05.898
her eyes swelling with tears.

00:01:07.383 --> 00:01:09.443
She says, "Grandmother Jack,

00:01:10.092 --> 00:01:11.756
I'm HIV-positive.

00:01:12.721 --> 00:01:15.587
I've been living with HIV
for the past four years.

00:01:16.019 --> 00:01:18.208
My husband left me a year ago.

00:01:18.645 --> 00:01:19.943
I have two kids

00:01:20.683 --> 00:01:22.013
under the age of five.

00:01:22.343 --> 00:01:23.538
I'm unemployed.

00:01:23.981 --> 00:01:27.543
I can hardly take care of my children."

00:01:28.211 --> 00:01:30.714
Tears are now flowing down her face.